      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition. It has been meticulously cared for, with a flawless exterior finish and an interior that still looks and smells like new. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, from the powerful, smooth-running engine to the seamless transmission. There are absolutely no signs of wear, scratches, or mechanical issues. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been maintained to the highest possible standard, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from a brand-new car.",
