    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While it remains mechanically sound and has been regularly serviced, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. The interior is clean but exhibits visible wear on the driver's seat upholstery and some scuffing on the plastic trim. It is a solid, honest car that runs well and is ready for the road, though it lacks the pristine finish of a newer model.",
