    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This vehicle is ready for a new lease on life and offers a fantastic opportunity for someone looking for a restoration project or a reliable source of parts. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a diamond in the rough with plenty of potential for the right owner. Grab this budget-friendly find and make it your own!",
