    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the perfect balance of performance and practicality for a discerning driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium leather upholstery has been treated regularly and shows only light bolstering wear on the driver\u2019s side. All electronic components, from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car has been fastidiously maintained with a complete service log available for review. It features a set of tires with excellent tread remaining and recently serviced brakes that provide firm, confident stopping power. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. This is a non-smoker vehicle that has been garage-kept, offering a turnkey driving experience for its next owner.",
